<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 01:01:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Rho Motion 称，7 月份全球电动汽车销量增长 21%，中国创下 2024 年最大增幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-21-july-china-records-biggest-jump-2024-rho-motion-says-2024-08-12/</link><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 周一表示，尽管欧洲需求下降，但得益于中国今年最强劲的增长，7 月份全电动和插电式混合动力汽车的全球销量同比增长 21%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 23:06:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-up-21-july-china-records-biggest-jump-2024-rho-motion-says-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：新发现的市场平静等待动荡的考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-08-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 21:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>欧佩克下调石油需求增长预期，凸显10月加息的困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/opec-cuts-2024-oil-demand-growth-forecast-citing-china-2024-08-12/</link><description>OPEC 周一下调了 2024 年全球石油需求增长预测，理由是对中国的预期疲软，这一下调凸显了更广泛的 OPEC+ 集团在 10 月份起增产方面面临的困境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 10:46:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/opec-cuts-2024-oil-demand-growth-forecast-citing-china-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>越南新任党总书记将于下周访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-newly-appointed-party-chief-set-visit-china-next-week-2024-08-12/</link><description>三名知情官员告诉路透社，越南最高领导人苏林将于下周访问中国，这是他自八月初被任命为执政的共产党总书记以来的首次出访。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 08:45:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnams-newly-appointed-party-chief-set-visit-china-next-week-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国将针对朝鲜导弹和网络威胁举行年度演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-over-norths-missile-cyber-threats-2024-08-12/</link><description>官员周一表示，韩国和美国将于下周开始年度夏季军事演习，以提高应对朝鲜武器和网络威胁的能力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 06:47:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-over-norths-missile-cyber-threats-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>随着低空经济加速发展，中国试验货运无人机和空中出租车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-test-flies-biggest-cargo-drone-low-altitude-economy-takes-off-2024-08-12/</link><description>周末，工程师们派出了中国迄今为止最大的货运无人机进行试运行，同时一架直升机出租车在即将开通的通往上海的 100 公里（62 英里）航线上飞上了天空，为中国不断扩大的低空运输奠定了新的里程碑——高原经济。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:53:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-test-flies-biggest-cargo-drone-low-altitude-economy-takes-off-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>黄岩岛空难事件后菲律宾敦促中国缓和紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-file-protest-with-china-over-air-force-incident-over-south-china-sea-2024-08-12/</link><description>菲律宾周一敦促北京重视缓和南海紧张局势的呼吁，此前菲律宾称其空军在两国同意更好地管理海上争端后采取了“非常危险”的行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 03:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-file-protest-with-china-over-air-force-incident-over-south-china-sea-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲足球周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-08-12/</link><description>本周亚洲足球的谈话要点：</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/week-asian-football-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院驳回媒体大亨黎智英推翻定罪的请求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-by-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-overturn-conviction-2024-08-12/</link><description>香港最高法院周一一致驳回了推翻媒体大亨黎智英和其他六名民主运动人士2019年未经授权集会定罪的请求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 02:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-dismisses-bid-by-media-tycoon-jimmy-lai-overturn-conviction-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院推迟中国佳兆业集团清算听证会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-08-12/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求佳兆业集团清算的请愿书的听证会推迟至 9 月 9 日，这使得这家陷入困境的中国开发商有更多时间与一些债券持有人就其债务重组计划达成协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 01:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-kaisa-group-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-by-hong-kong-court-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>央行与多头对峙，中国国债市场动荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</link><description>中国央行一再警告称，随着投资者追逐政府债券、逃离动荡的股票和不断下滑的房地产市场，可能存在破坏稳定的泡沫风险。</description><pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 00:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-bond-market-rattled-central-bank-squares-off-with-bond-bulls-2024-08-12/</guid></item><item><title>外交部长表示，中国支持伊朗捍卫安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</link><description>据中国外交部的一份声明称，中国外交部长王毅周日在电话中告诉伊朗代理外长，中国支持伊朗捍卫其“主权、安全和民族尊严”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 11:21:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-iran-defending-security-says-foreign-minister-2024-08-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国空军的行动“非法”、“鲁莽”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</link><description>中国表示，菲律宾扰乱了其训练，并指责马尼拉“非法侵入”其领空。</description><pubDate>Sun, 11 Aug 2024 06:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-actions-china-air-force-illegal-reckless-2024-08-11/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与中国就南海问题进行贸易指责</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</link><description>这是自2022年小费迪南德·马科斯总统就职以来菲律宾首次抱怨中国飞机的危险行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 09:26:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-condemns-china-air-force-dangerous-acts-south-china-sea-2024-08-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国火箭解体使1000多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</link><description>分析人士周五表示，中国的一枚火箭级本周在太空中解体，产生了 700 多块碎片，使地球轨道交通繁忙区域的 1000 多颗卫星和其他物体面临危险碰撞的风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 22:03:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinese-rockets-breakup-puts-over-1000-satellites-other-objects-risk-2024-08-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>